Name: PaWz 400 Pcs 60x60cm Charcoal Pet Puppy Dog Toilet Training Pads Ultra Absorbent
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Our dog pads are highly absorbent and won't leak or spread. They are made with Flash-Dry technology that instantly turns liquid into a gel, preventing leaks that can damage your floor or carpet. These Dog Pads instantly eliminate odors and contains a fresh lavender scent for lasting freshness.

  • Flash-dry technology instantly turns liquid into gel
  • Won't spread and won't leak
  • Helps to protect your floor and carpet
  • Fresh Lavender Scent
  • Eliminates odors
  • Transforms bad smells into a pleasant scent
  • Keeps your home smelling clean
  • Black potty pads, so your pets mess stays discrete and you never see a yellow stain on a white puppy pad in your home
  • Odor Elimination with carbon technology for all-day use to ensure your home stays fresh
  • Ultra Absorbent

How to use a dog pad:
Unfold and place the pad, plastic side down, in a confined area, away from your dog's bed and food.
Place your dog on the pad several times so he can smell the pad and get used to it.
While your dog is eliminating on the pad, use a phrase like "go potty" so that eventually you can use the command and your dog will understand what it means.  
Immediately after the dog eliminates on the pad, reward him with praise and a treat.
If your dog has an accident, bring him back to the pad immediately. Continue bringing your dog back to the pad to reinforce that this is the place to go potty.
Dispose of soiled pads and replace as needed.To complete house training, gradually move the pad closer to the door and finally outside.

SPECIFICATION
  • Material: Non-woven fabric
  • Size: 60x60cm
  • Quantity: 400pcs
PACKAGE CONTENTS
  • 400x Puppy Training Pads

Name: PaWz Dog Ramp For Car Suv Travel Stair Step Foldable Portable Lightweight Ladder
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Look after your dog with the Foldable Pet Ramp. Help your dog get in and out of cars, up to their favourite spot or even use it for their very own obstacle course. Go out on adventures knowing your dog is being looked after and can easily join you in the car.

Your dog will move safely up and down the ramp with the ridges along the walking surface. Reduce the stress on their bones and joints rather than letting them jump from higher places. It is perfect for your elderly dog or even just to help an injured dog. It can even give independence to your small dog who needs to be lifted to or moved down from higher places.

The foldable and lightweight design means it can be stored easily and is very space saving. You can just leave it in the back of your car or keep it in a cupboard at home. With a carry handle, you can move this anywhere.

Made of heavy-duty plastic, this will last even robust use. It is slip resistant and can connect to almost any kind of surface. If it gets dirty you can easily wash it down with a hose and leave it to dry.

Key Features:

  • Lightweight and foldable
  • Heavy-duty performance
  • Curved shape
  • Safety latch
  • Handy handle
  • Non-slip bottom
  • Fits all vehicles

Look after your dog with the Foldable Pet Ramp. Help your dog get in and out of cars, up to their favourite spot or even use it for their very own obstacle course. Go out on adventures knowing your dog is being looked after and can easily join you in the car.

Description:
DESCRIPTION

Help your pet calm down let them keep the stress away with our Anxiety-free Calming Jacket. No more need for toxic sedatives or medication when they are experiencing nervousness or depression.

You must be wondering how does it do it? Wear your pet with one and form a tight fit around their body and let the pressure do the rest. It wraps around the chest till the legs to give them a sense of warmth to make them feel they are protected it's this sensation that calms them down.

We have made it go easy on your pets’ skin its breathable material offers a soft and comfortable experience. Even if they are wearing it for long this jacket will not hurt them.

Very easy to put on adjust it on their body and tight it up using the Velcro straps. If you are feeling confused please follow the provided instruction manual.

Pet products expect durability which is why our calming jacket is made of cotton and nylon. Its sturdy construction extends life.

Name: PaWz Luxury Elevated Sofa Anti-slip Raised Dog Cat Beds Couch Kitten Lounge
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Your dog may sleep anywhere but they will be far happier having a space to call their own. This elevated dog bed is as stylish as your own bed. Such luxury. Wow.

As the saying goes ‘healthy dog happy dog’. The raised dog bed will stop any moisture build-up underneath the bed. A cleaner and comfier sleep for your new puppy or old dog.

Your new dog bed is breathable in summer and warm in winter. Buy one bed to use throughout the entire year. The comfy foam bed will keep them coming back.

This raised dog bed is inspired by the modern Scandinavian minimalism that started in the 1950s. It wouldn’t look out of place in a current fashion catalogue.

The non-slip feet pads will protect your floor and stop the bed sliding as your dog jumps on and off their new bed. Unless you have one of the biggest dog breeds the 50kg weight limit has you covered.

Key Features

  • Modern style
  • Elevated base
  • Comfortable backrest
  • Soft velvet upholstery
  • 20D Sponge padding
  • Thick MDF frame
  • Solid wood legs
  • Non-slip feet pads
  • Removable cover
  • Machine washable
SPECIFICATION

Material: MDF 20D Sponge and pine

Weight capacity: Up to 50kg 

Colour: Grey

Name: PaWz Orthopedic Dog Bed With Memory Foram Warm Mattress Plush Large
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Your pet will rest easy on this orthopaedic memory foam pet bed. Buy it now to provide a calm and comforting bed for your favourite pet.

One of the big problems with any pet bed is cleaning. This PaWz bed has an easily removable cover with a zip. Simply throw the cover in the washing machine and it will come out like nice and clean.

This pet bed removes the need to have a separate bed for summer and winter. Memory foam has the benefits of retaining heat in winter and being cool in summer.

With bolstered sides, your pet will sleep even easier and wake up refreshed to enjoy your company. The memory foam takes good care of your pet’s back and spine.

All your pets will love this memory foam bed. Dogs, cats, goats, guinea pigs, definitely not fish and elephants are sadly too big.

One big worry is your pet destroying their new bed. The cover is bite and dirt resistant. It is also gentle on their nose and paws. The fabric is skin friendly and easy to use.

Key Features:

  • Memory foam filling
  • Ergonomic posture
  • Perfect body contour
  • Supportive bolster
  • Detachable cover
  • Machine washable

  • Anti-slip bottom
  • Large padded bolster for comfort
  • ALL season use
